.TH DEVCLEAN 1 "July 2026" "devclean 0.1.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
devclean \- scan and clean developer cache directories
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B devclean
.RI [ command ] [ options ] [ targets ]
.SH DESCRIPTION
devclean scans common developer cache directories and can remove them safely.
.SH COMMANDS
.TP
.B scan
Scan known caches.
.TP
.B analyze
Analyze cache growth and provide recommendations.
.TP
.B clean
Delete selected caches.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.B --report markdown|html|csv|json
Emit a report in the requested format.
.TP
.B --dry-run
Show what would be removed without deleting anything.
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
.B devclean scan
Scan the default cache catalog.
.TP
.B devclean analyze --report markdown
Generate a markdown analysis report.
